or or similar is required. Experience with Microsoft Azure is required. Specifically, Azure Key Vault, Azure Kubernetes Service, Azure Dedicated HSM, Blob Storage, Azure Backup, Azure Functions, Virtual Machines, Service Fabric and Container Instances. Experience with Python, Bash, and/or PowerShell with a focus on automation and infrastructure as code. Experience with JS, Java, C# is preferred. Experience writing Terraform and Ansible code. Understanding of Linux operating systems at a detailed level including processes, memory allocation, subsystems and networking. Expert-level troubleshooting skills. Experience designing, building, and implementing continuous integration pipelines using Jenkins, Azure DevOps, TeamCity or similar. Comfortable with Git, Jira, and similar tools. Experience with cloud and on-premises TCP/IP networking. Experience with managing databases, specifically MySQL and Oracle. Bakkt is devoted to having diversity in its workforce and is proud to be an equal opportunity employer. Bakkt does not make any employment decisions based on race, color, religion, sex, national origin, veteran status, disability, age, sexual orientation, gender identity of any other characteristic protected by law Apply for this job ???????????????????????? New York City, NY ", 
